title: Refactor: Decoupled Chaincode Logic from PTE Execution Engine
body: Removed chaincode-specific logic to generate arguments from `pte-execRequest.js`. That logic is now in folders under `ccArgumentsGenerators`, with the subfolder name corresponding to a `ccType`.
